  <num>47-3307</num>
  <heading>Certain suits forbidden.</heading>
  <formerly-cited-as>DC ST 1981 § 47-3307</formerly-cited-as>
  <text>No suit shall be filed to enjoin the assessment or collection by the District of Columbia or any of its officers, agents, or employees of any tax.</text>
